<local:MyHint Margin="0,0,0,15" Text="本教程同样适用于其他被误删的文件！" IsWarn="False" />
<local:MyHint Margin="0,0,0,15" Text="此教程仅保证对Windows 10以上的系统有效！" IsWarn="True" />
<local:MyCard Title="简介">
    <StackPanel Margin="25,40,23,15">
        <TextBlock Margin="0,0,0,0" LineHeight="17" 
                    Text="MSDerfender有时是你保护电脑的得力助手，有时又会抽风误删你的PCL2。本教程将详细的讲述你应该怎么避免此情况。" />
    </StackPanel>
</local:MyCard>

<local:MyCard Title="添加排除项" Margin="0,0,0,15">
	<StackPanel Margin="25,40,23,15">
        <Grid>
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,20,0,4" Width="400"
                        Text="1. 找到你任务栏上MSDerfender的图标，点击它。如果找不到图标，也可以点击下方的按钮打开安全中心。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <Image Height="275" Margin="450,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/06/28/659e774fdf60a61b.png" />
        </Grid>

        <local:MyButton Margin="0,4,0,8" Width="200" Height="35"
                    Text="打开MSDerfender"  ToolTip="仅对Windows 10以上系统有效！" EventType="打开文件" EventData="explorer|ms-settings:windowsdefender" />

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,20,0,4" Width="400"
                        Text="2. 进入主界面，点击“病毒和威胁防护”选项卡。（侧栏与中心均可点击！）" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <Image Height="275" Margin="450,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/06/28/cd3e5026b51e6490.png" />
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,20,0,0" Width="400"
                        Text="3. 找到“病毒和威胁防护设置”，单击“管理设置”。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <Image Height="275" Margin="450,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Right" Source="https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/06/28/8f8f6fd24798e92a.png" />
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,20,0,4" Width="400"
                        Text="4. 进入二级页面，使用鼠标滚轮向下滑动，找到“排除项”，单击“添加或删除排除项”。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <Image Height="275" Margin="450,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/06/28/fc5514927f6687a2.png" />
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,20,0,4" Width="400"
                        Text="5. 进入三级页面，点击“添加排除项”。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <Image Height="275" Margin="450,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/06/28/dfa9b4403091c938.png" />
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,20,0,4" Width="400"
                        Text="6.在跳出来的选项卡中，点击“文件夹”。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <Image Height="275" Margin="450,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/06/28/f491f9c6ff42cb86.png" />
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,20,0,4" Width="400"
                        Text="7.确保你的PCL2启动器主程序（Plain Craft Launcher 2.exe）在你的MC文件夹中，在跳出来的资源管理器窗口中选择你的MC文件夹。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
            <Image Height="275" Margin="450,0,0,0" HorizontalAlignment="Center" Source="https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2023/06/28/0c5d05f684474d32.png" />
        </Grid>

        <Grid Margin="0,20,0,4">
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,20,0,4" Width="400"
                        Text="8.完成！以后PCL2就不会被误删了。" HorizontalAlignment="Left" />
        </Grid>
    </StackPanel>
</local:MyCard>

